The Good Diabetes Care in Schools Award is awarded by Diabetes UK based on
information supplied by the school, parents of children attending the school
and at least one independent healthcare professional at the time of award.
School resources, practices and management may change at any time for reasons
out of our control. Diabetes UK accepts no responsibility for any claims,
losses or any type of damage whatsoever arising out of any reliance on an
award, or its decision to make or not make an award to a school.
